---
const whatsappLink = "https://wa.me/919601330716?text=Hi%20Nikhil%2C%20I%20want%20to%20build%20a%20project%20with%20you.";
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">
      About Me
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Education</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
              Master of Computer Applications (MCA)
            </h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Indus University</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Pursuing, Expected 2027</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">
              Bachelor of Computer Applications (BCA)
            </h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600">VNSGU</p>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">CGPA 7.7/10 | 2022-2025</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Professional Summary</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          I am a <strong>freelance Full-Stack MERN and AI developer in Gujarat</strong>, working with founders and growing teams across <strong>Umbergaon, Vapi, Valsad, and Ahmedabad</strong>.
          I build production-ready web platforms with <strong>React, Astro, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB</strong>, then integrate intelligent AI workflows using <strong>LangGraph, RAG, and LLM tooling</strong>.
          My recent work includes <strong>Servielliance</strong> (service marketplace), <strong>TimeCapsule</strong> (AI memory assistant), and multi-agent systems for automated research and content generation.
          If you need one developer who can own product UI, backend APIs, and AI automation with clear communication, I can deliver end to end.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Need a developer who can own delivery end to end?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">
        Let's discuss your goals and map the fastest path to launch.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <a href={whatsappLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white text-slate-900 font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">Let's build your project</a>
        <a href={whatsappLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-400 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">Get a free consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
